### URL: /firefox/smart-window/

smart-window-page-title = Smart Window
smart-window-page-desc = Smart Window: exploring the future through our values

# "Coming Soon" badge/pill label
smart-window-coming-soon = Coming Soon

smart-window-heading = Smart Window: Built for choice & control
smart-window-description-bold = The web is changing, and sitting it out doesn't help anyone.
smart-window-description = We were founded under the mission that the web should be open, fast, secure and people first. As AI becomes a larger part of the web, we see a clear role: to shape it in ways that support choice and keep the internet open and accessible to all. With Smart Window we'll do this through:
smart-window-benefit-optin = A fully opt-in experience
smart-window-benefit-choice = Features that protect your choice
smart-window-benefit-transparency = More transparency around how your data is used
smart-window-community = Our success has always been driven by a community of users and developers. Let's explore how AI can serve the open web together.

# Waitlist state (unsupported country)
smart-window-waitlist-signup = Sign up to receive updates and to be among the first to try it
smart-window-waitlist-cta = Join the waitlist
smart-window-waitlist-success-heading = You're on the list!
smart-window-waitlist-success-description = If you haven't previously confirmed a subscription to a Mozilla-related newsletter, you may have to do so. Please check your inbox or your spam filter for an email from us.

# Firefox Desktop state (supported country)
smart-window-enable-heading = Enable Smart Window
smart-window-enable-description = Sign in to your Firefox account to enable Smart Window and explore the future of the open web.
smart-window-enable-cta = Sign in & Enable Smart Window

# Non-Firefox state (supported country)
smart-window-download-heading = Get Firefox with Smart Window
smart-window-download-description = Download Firefox to get started with Smart Window — an opt-in AI experience built for choice, control, and transparency.
smart-window-download-cta = Download Firefox

# Shared
smart-window-privacy-notice = I'm okay with Mozilla handling my info as explained in this <a href="{ $url }">Privacy Notice</a>
